data.text:
Walid Elmusrati is an Lifestyle Influencer, Content Creator and an Actor with 15 years of Expertise.

Featured in the Reality TV show "Bela Houdood" with the Lebanese actress and singer Cyrine Abdelnour where his dailies were followed by cameras for six months. Walid has also acted in the latest music video of the star Dominique Hourani.

In the past years, Walid travelled the world creating amazing content for his followers showcasing the best places to visit and cultures around the globe.
